# Production Hardening & Platform Quality Audit

> **Analogy**: Floors 1-2 must be senior expert-level before building the skyscraper. Every foundational page must be bug-free, performant, and premium UX before adding new features.

**Budget constraint**: No backend service changes. Staying on Supabase + Vercel + Cloudflare R2.

---

## Critical Bugs & Fixes (Must do before anything else)

### 1. `useCallback` in JSX (React Rules Violation)
**File**: [app/watch/[id]/WatchClient.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Walt%20&%20Carter/.gemini/antigravity/playground/sonic-zenith/app/watch/%5Bid%5D/WatchClient.tsx) line ~190  
Calling `useCallback()` directly inside JSX is illegal in React — hooks cannot be called conditionally or inside render. This will cause a runtime crash.  
**Fix**: Hoist the callback to the component body.

### 2. Missing `import React` / `useCallback` at component level
`useCallback` is imported from `'react'` but used in JSX — this is a React Rules of Hooks violation.

### 3. `Pause` icon not imported in VideoPlayer
[VideoPlayer.tsx](file:///C:/GOLive/components/VideoPlayer.tsx) imports `Play, Pause` — need to double-check `Pause` is in the lucide-react import.

